Privacy Policy for Orų Stotelės

Effective Date: 2024-01-28

Thank you for choosing Orų Stotelės! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information remains secure. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information collected by Orų Stotelės and how that information is used.

Information Collection:
Orų Stotelės does not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information about its users. We believe in a privacy-first approach and strive to create a safe and enjoyable user experience without compromising your personal data.

Permissions:
Orų Stotelės may request certain permissions to access device features necessary for its core functionality. These permissions include but are not limited to:

List of Permissions:
INTERNET
ACCESS_INTERNET_STATE

These permissions are solely used to provide you with the intended services of the app and are not utilized to gather any personal information.

Analytics and Crash Reporting:
Orų Stotelės may use analytics and crash reporting tools to improve the app's performance and identify issues. However, these tools are configured to collect only anonymized and aggregated data. This information is used solely for the purpose of enhancing the user experience and resolving technical issues.

Changes to this Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update our Privacy Policy as needed. Any changes will be communicated through the app or our website. It is recommended to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please open an issue at https://github.com/tunaitis/weatherstations/issues

By using Orų Stotelės, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Thank you for trusting Orų Stotelės with your privacy.
